Feature selection via glmnet

Source: R/model-feature-selection.R
featsel_glmnet.Rd

Feature selection via glmnet

Usage

featsel_glmnet(
  model,
  S = "lambda.1se",
  plot = TRUE,
  seed = 123,
  trace.it = 1,
  type.measue = "auc",
  ...
)

Arguments

model

model

S

S

plot

plot

seed

seed

trace.it

trace.it p

type.measue

type.measue

...

Additional argumentos for glmnet::cv.glmnet

Examples


data("credit_woe")

m <- glm(bad ~ ., family = binomial, data = credit_woe)

featsel_glmnet(m)
